@TaskManager.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5226

### Auth - Login (public)
POST {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Auth - Validate Token
POST {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/validate
Content-Type: application/json

"seu-jwt-token-aqui"

### User - Register (public)
POST {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/user/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### User - Get All (requires Authorization)
GET {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/user
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### User - Get By Id (requires Authorization - own profile only)
GET {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/user/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Task - Get All (requires Authorization)
GET {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/task
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Task - Get By Id (requires Authorization)
GET {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/task/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Task - Create (requires Authorization)
POST {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/task
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Nova tarefa",
  "description": "Descrição da tarefa"
}

### Task - Update (requires Authorization)
PATCH {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/task/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Título atualizado",
  "isCompleted": true
}

### Task - Delete (requires Authorization)
DELETE {{TaskManager.Api_HostAddress}}/api/task/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
